242
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,640
and benefit your company.

243
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:24,760
What choice will you make?

244
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:27,440
Thank about it.

245
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,960
