283
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:41,760
Yes.

284
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,040
I’m your shareholder.

285
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,840
But I can tell you right now

286
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:48,000
